utilities

Class Tester

  • java.lang.Object
    • utilities.Tester

  • public class Tester
extends java.lang.Object
    The tester class is the driver for the program and takes user input to conduct different types of sorts on shapes. The class then prints out the results of the sort in descending order and should display the time it took to do the chosen sorting algorithm.
    Version:
    1.0 Created on February 19, 2020
    Author:
    Casey Majandog
